{"tid":2512103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殺人警員林偉榮　裁定罪成　但仍然逍遙法外　警方遲遲不拘捕","createTime":"2021-05-01T12:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T20:13:46.000Z","uid":261647,"like":649,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a9da83ba860403adcb515f98c3e332fb61544a","tid":2512103,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=236360148281569&amp;id=108470987737153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D236360148281569%26id%3D108470987737153&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=2640760f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=236360148281569&amp;id=108470987737153</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcK4gVsRF1oT674NpzYDPaBDJ2s2tyW7oqAveEWU42LPp?filename=158H9vk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F158H9vk.jpg&h=9d415836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：醜惡的忠誠勇毅<br />\n<br />\n裁定不合法殺人，疑犯黑警林偉榮仍逍遙法外! !<br />\n<br />\n殺人填命 ! 要求立即逮捕殺人警歸案 !<br />\n<br />\n顧家的士司機陳輝旺(65歲)因車資與乘客爭執，到場警員林偉榮將陳箍頸扯高，雙腳凌空，引致頸椎移位而死。2018年死因庭4男1女陪審團以3比2裁定的哥不合法被殺，證據確鑿，罪無可恕，但警方故意拖延時間遲遲沒有逮捕殺人警，繩之以法，難慰無辜死者在天之靈，彰顯公義，踏入2021年仍未拉人，警方欲「丟淡」件事，要求立即逮捕殺人警歸案 !"},{"pid":"13ca4e1e9c54b41026d4ca6f065018872df0d475","tid":2512103,"uid":156073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c988cbca390a1f72ddb7e4befd14196ad580010e","tid":2512103,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/k